Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:20.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:28.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:33.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:38.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:43.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:04.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:14.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:21.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:27.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:34.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:38.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:20.16,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.08,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:28.21,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光暈  浮現於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:33.42,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,未見未知的陽光  會將誰照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:38.18,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,我親愛的伙伴  就算沉浸於悲傷也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:43.14,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.44,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  來伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.81,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿過這片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.02,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  衝擊全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.65,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.32,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,緊盯著世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:04.16,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,當小小胸膛填滿了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:14.09,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,琥珀之夢  朝著約定的地點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:21.47,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,對你的關心關愛  比這天空更寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:27.60,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,無限擴張  永無止境
Comment: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:34.53,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:38.41,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
