Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I want to go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:56.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}住み慣れたこの街を出てゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}新しい世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:03.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}まだ見ぬ色を　探しに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:04.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I can not do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:10.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}素直になれないこともあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}あの虹の向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:16.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}行ってみたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:24.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}頭に浮かんだイメージを抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:30.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I will never ever give up halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:38.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}どこまでも　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:45.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I wanna make my life shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:56.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}輝くよ　あの虹の向こうまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.87,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想要出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:56.00,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}離開這熟悉的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.17,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}去探索新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:03.09,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}尋找從未見過的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:04.55,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:10.52,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}有時也會不夠坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.65,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}那彩虹的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:16.48,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想試著去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:24.11,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}記住浮現在頭腦中的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:30.95,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我永遠不會半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:38.55,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不論到哪裡  不論走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:45.55,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想讓自己的生命更閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:56.48,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}釋放光芒吧  直到那彩虹的彼端
